It has been six months now since the move from SolB to skyfire, and the bump in the spawn time from 36-72 hrs to 120-145 hrs.  In SolB, Ragefire had a chance to spawn over a majority of the camp time. <br>
<br>
Our lotto proposal to do away with these insane camp times did not win universal support so now we have this odd mix of folks camping solo, multiple folks with scouts watching for him at once, guilds camping skyfire with a full killing force, and lots of GM involvement.  The spawn has yet to degenerate to the level of ugliness I've heard about on other servers though, and for that emarr can be proud.<br>
